title: Some of the dumbest ways people have died in Zelda Breath of the Wild (15 Gifs)
text:

The new Zelda: Breath of the Wild is a harder game. Gone are the plethora of free hearts and backup fairies (what a sentence that was). As such, there have been some pretty humorous deaths taking place. Kotaku collected a few fun stories together. Here are a few. 2
